<Layout title="Google AI Mode Optimisation UK | Rank4AI" description="How to optimise for Google AI Mode. The new AI-powered search tab in Google, powered by Gemini 2.5. UK guide from Rank4AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Google AI Mode Optimisation</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Google AI Mode is a new AI-powered tab in Google Search, powered by Gemini 2.5. When activated, it replaces traditional search results with a single AI-generated answer. No organic results are shown.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This is different from AI Overviews. AI Overviews sit above traditional results. AI Mode replaces them entirely.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What AI Mode Means for UK Businesses</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">When someone uses AI Mode to find a service provider, the AI builds a single answer from multiple sources. The businesses it recommends are the ones it understands clearly, trusts consistently, and can confidently cite.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This is the same Five Signal Model that applies across all AI platforms. Identity Clarity, Subject Authority, Meaning Architecture, Ecosystem Validation and Signal Consistency.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">How to Prepare</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The businesses that will appear in AI Mode are the ones building AI search visibility now. The same work that gets you recommended by ChatGPT and Perplexity will get you recommended by Google AI Mode.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Build the connected digital presence. Make sure AI can find, understand and trust your business from multiple independent sources. That is the baseline for every AI platform, including AI Mode.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-4">Check your AI Mode readiness</h2>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
